h\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim\">4. Truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/#5_Mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_lon_va_mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_nho_la_thu_khong_the_thieu_khi_lam_phim\" title=\"5. M\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa nh\u1ecf l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim\">5. M\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa nh\u1ecf l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/#6_Dung_so_ap_luc_khi_lam_phim\" title=\"6. \u0110\u1eebng s\u1ee3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi l\u00e0m phim\">6. \u0110\u1eebng s\u1ee3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi l\u00e0m phim<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/#7_Dieu_can_ghi_nho_khi_lam_phim_luon_luon_phai_linh_hoat\" title=\"7. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb khi l\u00e0m phim: lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i linh ho\u1ea1t\">7. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb khi l\u00e0m phim: lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i linh ho\u1ea1t<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/#8_Ghi_chu_chi_tiet_nhung_y_do_nghe_thuat_cua_nhom\" title=\"8. Ghi ch\u00fa chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m\">8. Ghi ch\u00fa chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/#Ket_Luan\" title=\"K\u1ebft Lu\u1eadn\">K\u1ebft Lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/strong>\u00a0\u2013 B\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tham gia cu\u1ed9c thi phim ng\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n e ng\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m? B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00ea-k\u00edp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh?<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\"><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong><\/a> s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb ngay v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n tr\u1ebb, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1ea7u tay.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Luu_y_bat_buoc_khi_lam_phim_ngan_ma_ai_cung_can_phai_biet\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\">8 L\u01b0u \u00fd b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Khi_lam_phim_ngan_ban_phai_la_mot_thuyen_truong_dung_nghia\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Hay_la_thuyen_truong_dung_nghia_chu_y_khi_lam_film\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><strong>1. Khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a:<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2265\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2265\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2265\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/dao-dien-phim-chinh-la-thuyen-truong.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/dao-dien-phim-chinh-la-thuyen-truong.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/dao-dien-phim-chinh-la-thuyen-truong-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/dao-dien-phim-chinh-la-thuyen-truong-768x512.jpg 768w\" alt=\"ch\u00fa khi khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn\" width=\"825\" height=\"550\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2265\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n phim ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 t\u1eeb k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n, l\u1ecbch s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1ecbch quay, t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m l\u00e0m phim, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf\u2026<\/p>\n<p>Tuy \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e8o l\u00e1i con thuy\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem nh\u00f3m l\u00e0m phim nh\u01b0 c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd. <strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn <\/strong>l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y n\u00f3i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, r\u00e0nh m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 suy ngh\u0129, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Khi_lam_phim_ngan_ban_can_biet_e-kip_cua_ban_la_ai\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Khi_lam_film_ngan_ban_can_biet_e-kip_cua_ban_la_ai\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>2. Khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft \u00ea-kip c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ai?<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2266\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2266\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2266\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ekip-lam-phim.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1456px) 100vw, 1456px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ekip-lam-phim.jpg 1456w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ekip-lam-phim-300x185.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ekip-lam-phim-768x475.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ekip-lam-phim-1024x633.jpg 1024w\" alt=\"Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn\" width=\"1456\" height=\"900\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2266\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ekip c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ai? B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Khi l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft Ekip m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ai? <\/strong>\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng? N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 do ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n, trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 phim \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Hay_luon_tao_dieu_kien_tot_nhat_cho_dien_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Chu_y_khi_lam_phim_Hay_luon_tao_dieu_kien_tot_nhat_cho_dien_vien\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>3. H\u00e3y lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean thi\u1ebfu tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i hay b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng trong m\u1eaft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt <strong>l\u01b0u \u00fd trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn<\/strong>\u00a0kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ef1a qu\u00e1 s\u01a1 s\u00e0i, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng b\u1ed9 phim v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi giao l\u01b0u, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean ch\u00ednh. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ebd n\u00ean b\u1ee9c tranh c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Truyen_cam_hung_la_dieu_khong_the_thieu_khi_lam_phim\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Truyen_cam_hung_la_dieu_khong_the_thieu_khi_lam_phim\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>4. Truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m phim, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u00ecm c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2267\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2267\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2267\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/truyen-cam-hung.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/truyen-cam-hung.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/truyen-cam-hung-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/truyen-cam-hung-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/truyen-cam-hung-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" alt=\"l\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t film\" width=\"825\" height=\"464\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2267\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00e3y truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o phim tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, truy\u1ec1n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho c\u1ea3 \u0111o\u00e0n phim. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u00ea-k\u00edp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u00e0 h\u0103ng say s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y<strong> ghi nh\u1edb khi l\u00e0m film ng\u1eafn<\/strong>\u00a0r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu sinh kh\u00ed, l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u00ean l\u00ean hay r\u1ea7u r\u0129, bu\u1ed3n t\u1ee7i, m\u1eb7t c\u00fai g\u1eb1m xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e2u.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_lon_va_mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_nho_la_thu_khong_the_thieu_khi_lam_phim\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_lon_va_mot_quyen_so_ghi_chu_nho_la_thu_khong_the_thieu_khi_lam_phim\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">5. M\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ec3n s\u1ed5 ghi ch\u00fa nh\u1ecf l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi l\u00e0m phim<\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Lo\u1ea1i nh\u1ecf d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi 10 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i l\u1edbn li\u1ec7t k\u00ea 100 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c l\u1eb7t v\u1eb7t, chi ti\u1ebft kh\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y cho phim.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u00a0<strong>h\u1eefu \u00edch cho vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m phim ng\u1eafn<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ef9 m\u1ea3i \u0111u\u1ed5i theo nh\u1eefng \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Dung_so_ap_luc_khi_lam_phim\"><\/span><em><span id=\"Dung_so_ap_luc_khi_lam_phim\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>6. \u0110\u1eebng s\u1ee3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi l\u00e0m phim<\/strong><\/span><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y th\u00f4i. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng lao v\u00e0o quay b\u1ed9 phim ngay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang\u00a0cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Dieu_can_ghi_nho_khi_lam_phim_luon_luon_phai_linh_hoat\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Dieu_can_ghi_nho_khi_lam_phim_luon_luon_phai_linh_hoat\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>7. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb khi l\u00e0m phim: lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i linh ho\u1ea1t<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Phim ra r\u1ea1p \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u1ee9 ba, kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh quay v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u1eadu k\u1ef3. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 phong c\u00e1ch ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 linh ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Ghi_chu_chi_tiet_nhung_y_do_nghe_thuat_cua_nhom\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><em><span id=\"Ghi_chu_chi_tiet_nhung_y_do_nghe_thuat_cua_nhom\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>8. Ghi ch\u00fa chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n, nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, trao \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t t\u1ea7n t\u1eadt v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf bu\u1ed5i quay.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i phim tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <em><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-lam-phim-quang-cao-tai-ha-noi.html\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m phim qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_Luan\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\">K\u1ebft Lu\u1eadn<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong>8 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u01b0u \u00fd khi quay phim ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1e